---
import { MapPin, Target, Settings } from '@lucide/astro';
---
<section id="about" class="py-16 md:py-20 px-4 md:px-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent mb-12">About Me</h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-10">
        <!-- Main Bio -->
        <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5 font-body text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">
                I'm a <strong>Web Developer</strong> focused on building responsive, performant websites and web applications. My work spans from vanilla HTML/CSS/JavaScript sites to modern frameworks like Astro and React, always prioritizing clean code and user experience.
            </p>
            
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">
                Currently, I freelance on custom web development projects including <strong>static sites with Mapbox integration</strong>, <strong>WordPress theme customization</strong> from Figma designs, and <strong>website maintenance</strong> with blog content generation and multi-language localization for international audiences.
            </p>
            
            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">
                My <strong>primary client is OneJourney Tours</strong>, where I handle website development, blog content generation with AI assistance, and multi-language localizations across 10+ languages to drive organic search traffic.
            </p>

            <p class="leading-relaxed text-base">
                Beyond development, I have hands-on experience with project management, QA testing, database design, and technical documentation. I hold industry certifications in <strong>Network Security, Java, and Databases</strong> from Certiport.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Info Sidebar -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Location -->
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-accent/20 dark:border-accent/30 bg-accent/5 dark:bg-accent/10">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <MapPin size={22} class="text-accent mt-1" aria-hidden="true" />
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-1 font-heading">Location</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 font-body">Philippines</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Focus Areas -->
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-accent/20 dark:border-accent/30 bg-accent/5 dark:bg-accent/10">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <Target size={22} class="text-accent mt-1" aria-hidden="true" />
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2 font-heading">Specializations</h4>
                        <ul class="text-xs space-y-1 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 font-body">
                            <li>• Web Development</li>
                            <li>• Static Sites & Mapbox</li>
                            <li>• WordPress Themes</li>
                            <li>• Localization</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Tools -->
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-accent/20 dark:border-accent/30 bg-accent/5 dark:bg-accent/10">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <Settings size={22} class="text-accent mt-1" aria-hidden="true" />
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm mb-2 font-heading">Tools I Use</h4>
                        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                            <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-accent/10 dark:bg-accent/20 text-accent font-sans">VS Code</span>
                            <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-accent/10 dark:bg-accent/20 text-accent font-sans">Figma</span>
                            <span class="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded bg-accent/10 dark:bg-accent/20 text-accent font-sans">Firebase</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
